OL,3,CBoy, 15, in hospital with serious
OL,4,Cinjuries after school stabbing
OL,6,FA 15-year-old boy is in hospital with
OL,7,Fserious injuries after being stabbed
OL,8,Fat his school.
OL,10,FPolice were alerted to the assault at
OL,11,FNottingham University Academy of
OL,12,FScience and Technology at around
OL,13,F1.36pm on Thursday.
OL,15,FThe teenager was taken to Queen's
OL,16,FMedical Centre and police believe the
OL,17,F"victim and suspect are known to each
OL,18,Fother".
OL,20,FA 15-year-old boy was arrested at the
OL,21,Fscene.
