OL,3,CBoy, 15, in hospital with serious
OL,4,Cinjuries after school stabbing
OL,6,FPolice said there is "no information
OL,7,Fat this point that this is linked to
OL,8,Fthe national 'School Wars' social
OL,9,Fmedia posts".
OL,11,FSuperintendent Chris Pearson said:
OL,12,F"This is obviously an unsettling
OL,13,Fincident to occur on school grounds,
OL,14,Fand we are working closely with
OL,15,FNottingham University Academy of
OL,16,FScience and Technology.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
