OL,3,CBoy, 15, in hospital with serious
OL,4,Cinjuries after school stabbing
OL,6,F"A 15-year-old boy has sustained a
OL,7,Fstab injury and been sent to Queen's
OL,8,FMedical Centre for treatment. His
OL,9,Finjuries are currently believed to be
OL,10,Fserious.
OL,12,F"His family will be supported by
OL,13,Fspecially trained officers while a
OL,14,Fthorough investigation is underway. A
OL,15,F15-year-old boy has been arrested in
OL,16,Fconnection with this incident.
OL,18,F"We know this is likely to cause alarm
OL,19,Fand distress across our local
OL,20,Fcommunity especially for parents and
OL,21,Fpupils in the area."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
