OL,3,CBoy, 15, in hospital with serious
OL,4,Cinjuries after school stabbing
OL,6,FHe continued: "I also want to stress
OL,7,Fthat there is no wider threat to any
OL,8,Fother pupils at the school. We will be
OL,9,Fworking closely with the school over
OL,10,Fthe coming days to establish what has
OL,11,Fhappened."
OL,26,@nD@OOU
